---
// src/components/StoryFamily.astro
---
<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white dark:bg-appleGray-900 border-t border-appleGray-200 dark:border-appleGray-800">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-16">
    <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
      <span class="text-indigo-500 font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Chapter 01</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">My Family</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-appleGray-600 dark:text-appleGray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">
        The foundation of everything I do. My family has been my constant support and my greatest inspiration. 
        These are the moments we cherish together, the bonds that tie us, and the memories that last a lifetime.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 w-full grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-6">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511895426328-dc8714191300?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Family Beach Day" class="zoomable w-full h-48 sm:h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1" />
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1476610182048-b716b8518aae?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Family Dinner" class="zoomable w-full h-48 sm:h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 mt-8 lg:mt-12" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
